metadata.description:
This final compilation, originally put together by an unknown person and spread on P2P networks, but now embraced by Monotonik as a good primer for our net.label's output up to around 2001, has more well-chosen releases on it.

As with previous compilations by the same person, a number of tracks (although less this time!) only normally available in .MOD form are here as .MP3s - check out the neat Substance track, more early Jiva, and a great melding of a bunch of MP3 releases into a cohesive compilation.

Track listing (items with * have only previously been available in .MOD form):

1. Mosaik - "Rubik"
2. Proem - "Romanian Fruit Bowl"
3. Lackluster - "Grind"*
4. Jiva - "Toasted"*
5. Phasmid - "The Heroine Of Goat Bells"
6. PBXO - "Autumn Week"
7. Aereal - "Metro Cammell"
8. Vae - "Sing, Silverduck, Sing"
9. Starmode - "TBTD (Zyad's Magic Carp Ride)"
10. Ckid - "TV People"
11. Lackluster - "21/01/01"
12. Super Science - "This Is Over By Inches"
13. Proswell - "0eo"
14. Substance - "Smart Identity Control"
15. Tim Koch - "Werdan"
16. Idmonster - "My Human Side"
